com.turing123.libs.android.resourcemanager

Class ResourceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.turing123.libs.android.resourcemanager.ResourceManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IResourceManager

    public class ResourceManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements IResourceManager
    This class provider resource manager function. The name of default resources directory is .TuringResource ,and resources include String, Audio File, Image File and gif File.

    When you uses RobotFrame, you should copy Turing Resource Directory to SDCard. At the same time, You can set your own resource directory by calling setCustomResourceDir(String). But Your resource directory must have struct of turing resource directory. As follows:

    The struct of a resource Dir:

    ../
      string/
      audio/
      drawable/
      gif/
      plugin/
